## Is it worth learning?

Based on your previous questions, your interests are:

* C++ development
* Backend systems
* Trading/HFT
* Linux
* PostgreSQL

Drogon aligns well with those interests. 
It lets you stay in the C++ ecosystem while building production-grade web services. 
If your goal is general web development jobs, Spring Boot or ASP.NET typically have a larger job market, but if you want high-performance C++ backend development, Drogon is a strong choice.


